videos.description: Auburn extends its lead as Allen Flanigan lofts it up top to Walker Kessler for the easy jam.

videos.description: Auburn big man Dylan Cardwell powers in the layup and lets the defense hear about it, leading to a technical foul.

videos.headline: Auburn's Cardwell gets tech after making layup over defender

videos.description: Auburn point guard Wendell Green Jr. throws the lob up top to Dylan Cardwell for the big two-handed jam.

videos.description: Auburn's K.D. Johnson picks Bijan Cortes' pocket in the backcourt and finishes the layup, firing up the crowd and forcing an Oklahoma timeout.

videos.description: Auburn's Wendell Green Jr. almost loses the ball, but gets it back and makes the pass from the floor to Walker Kessler for the and-1.

videos.description: Auburn improves to 20-1 as they get 23 points from Jabari Smith and 21 points from Walker Kessler.

videos.headline: Smith, Kessler combine for 43 in Auburn's win

videos.description: After an 86-68 victory over Oklahoma in the SEC/Big 12 Challenge, Walker Kessler says playing for the Tigers is "way more than my expectations."
videos.headline: Kessler thrilled to be playing for No. 1 Auburn
